- cs.LO (Optimization and Control): The paper proposes algorithms to compute upper and lower bounds on the distance between two sets of traces, which involves optimization and control techniques. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper presents new algorithms to compute distances between reachpipes, which involves data structures and algorithms. 
- cs.MS (Mathematical Software): The paper proposes new geometric insights to compute the worst-case and best-case distances between two polyhedral sets, which involves mathematical software. 
- cs.RO (Robotics): The paper's techniques for computing distances between reachpipes could be applicable in robotics, where uncertainty and noise are common.
